To Doc Spatz,<br><br>
Please remember this is not a religious discussion site.  I understand that this issue has stroke a chord with you, and I can appreciate that.  If you want to discuss this topic, I'm sure many other fine discussions sites exist.  I'm trying to end any heated discussion on this topic before it gets out of hand.  In a time when we need to keep this site alive, I don't want to see anyone leave due to being insulted on a topic not even related to the nature of this site.  I'm not saying this discussion doesn't have merit, nor am I saying you can't post (That is your right), and your view is always welcome.  I'm just saying that we should stick to the topic of Vietnam and its MANY facets here.<br><br>
Take it easy everyone, I'm just trying to use a diplomacy here!  My suggestions comes with the good intentions.
